  id: 7
  title: "Nh\u1EADt k\xFD anh trai #1"
  category: 2
  content: "H\xF4m nay em m\xECnh r\u1EDDi th\xE0nh ph\u1ED1 r\u1ED3i, c\xF3 l\u1EBD
    s\u1EBD kh\xF4ng g\u1EB7p l\u1EA1i n\u1EEFa. M\xECnh \u0111\xE3 \u0111\u1ED3ng
    \xFD th\u1EED thu\u1ED1c cho b\xE1c s\u0129 Edward, c\xF3 l\u1EBD \u0111\xE2y
    l\xE0 quy\u1EBFt \u0111\u1ECBnh \u0111\xFAng \u0111\u1EAFn. S\u1ED1 ti\u1EC1n
    m\xE0 b\xE1c s\u0129 Edward \u0111\u01B0a c\xF3 l\u1EBD s\u1EBD gi\xFAp n\xF3
    th\xE0nh c\xF4ng."
